parameters.description:
Shape (tail-index) parameter $\alpha > 0$.  Smaller values
produce heavier tails.  The mean exists only for $\alpha > 1$;
the variance only for $\alpha > 2$.

Shape parameter $k > 0$.  Values $k < 1$ give a
decreasing hazard; $k = 1$ gives the Exponential;
$k > 1$ gives an increasing hazard.

methods.extended:
